<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="B" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Brotherly" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Brotherly,</orth> adv., as becomes a brother: <cit><quote>I speak but b. of him,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ayl 1.1.162" default="NO" valid="yes">As I, 1, 162</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>to use your brothers b.</quote> <bibl n="shak. 3h6 4.3.38" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C IV, 3, 38</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>I love thee b.</quote> <bibl n="shak. cym 4.2.158" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. IV, 2, 158</bibl></cit>.
